{"word":"Μίδας","slug":"Μίδας","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n67679\" key=\"*mi/das\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Μίδας</orth> <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">[ῐ]</pron>, gen. <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ου</itype> or <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">α</itype>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Μίδης</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">εω</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Midas</title_>, proverbial for his wealth, <sense id=\"n67679.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ . . πλουτοίη . . Μίδεω καὶ Κινύρεω μάλιον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0266.tlg001:12:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Tyrt.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.6</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg003:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Epigr.\">Epigr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐὰν . . πλουτῇ Κινύρα τε καὶ Μίδα μᾶλλον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:660e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">660e</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-g